---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Time Zone Calculator - A Free Time Zone Converter"
  description="About page for Time Zone Calculator - a simple and free time zone converter tool to compare multiple time zones. Fast, accurate, and easy to use."
  keywords="time zone calculator, time zone converter, time zone compare, time zones, time zone app, global time compare, time zone tool, schedule across time zones, convert time, time zone comparer"
  canonicalURL="https://timezonecalculator.net/about"
  robots="index, follow"
>
  <main class="p-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <header>
        <h1>
          <i class="material-icons mr-1">info</i><span
            >About Time Zone Calculator</span>
        </h1>
        <br />
        <p>
          Time Zone Calculator is a simple and free time zone converter tool where you can select a
          time zone and a time, and then select one or multiple other time zones.
          The tool will then output what the selected time is in those other time
          zones.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>
          This tool is great for anyone who needs to know what time it is
          somewhere else, or in many other places. Great for setting up meetings
          across multiple areas, planning travel, scheduling long-distance phone calls, or just staying in sync.
        </p>
      </header>
      <br/>
      <h2>How to Use Time Time Zone Calculator:</h2>
      <p>Below are instructions on how to use the time zone comparison tool on this website.</p>
      <br/>
      <ol class="text-left border border-dashed p-6">
        <li>1. Navigate to our homepage at <a href="/" >https://timezonecalculator.net</a>.</li>
        <br/>
        <li>2. Select a "From" time zone.  This is the time zone you want to compare to others.</li>
        <br/>
        <li>3. Select a time for the "From" time zone.</li>
        <br/>
        <li>4. Select one or multiple "To" time zones.</li>
        <br/>
        <li>5. Click the "Compare Time Zones" button.</li>
        <br/>
        <section class="border-green-600 text-center">
          <p >Once these steps are completed, there will be an output of time zone comparisons.  There will be a new line for every added "To" time zone.</p>
        </section>
      </ol>
      <br />
      <p>Thank you for visiting this website!</p>
      <br/>
      <section>
        <h2>Back to Home Page</h2>
        <p>To use this tool, go back to the homepage.</p>
        <br />
        <p>
          <a href="/"
            ><i class="material-icons">undo</i><span
              class="text-xl font-semibold">Back to Home Page</span
            >
          </a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

